{"tid":242514,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（集思廣益）健康早餐分享","createTime":"2017-05-14T03:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T03:46:52.000Z","uid":23112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"702cae51d100f7c0c3d75c0b21c9d32b589a970d","tid":242514,"uid":23112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:35:04.000Z","msg":"有咩健康早餐可以分享下，最好可以早一日預備定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  朝早本身已經要早起身 唔想更早起身煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時我會食<br />\n一個橙加一隻全蛋 但唔知一早食橙會唔會對胃唔好<br />\n一條粟米加一隻全蛋<br />\n而家諗住整毛豆加蛋做早餐"},{"pid":"e9eaaf5f6d9343e243eeabf613cc505208e6ec27","tid":242514,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩健康早餐可以分享下，最好可以早一日預備定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  朝早本身已經要早起身 唔想更早起身煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時我會食<br />\n一個橙加一隻全蛋 但唔知一早食橙會唔會對胃唔好<br />\n一條粟米加一隻全蛋<br />\n而家諗住整毛豆加蛋做早餐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n橙好酸食完唔會胃痛咩<br />\n整三文治<br />\n芝士火腿咁擺落雪櫃<br />\n第二日喺雪櫃拎走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5dca9479738505552776c019ee0dcd350e95865","tid":242514,"uid":65893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:39:11.000Z","msg":"我最多都係三文治+果醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a73c96313a0e2d51e1ef17e1f89984912ba6182","tid":242514,"uid":23112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩健康早餐可以分享下，最好可以早一日預備定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  朝早本身已經要早起身 唔想更早起身煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時我會食<br />\n一個橙加一隻全蛋 但唔知一早食橙會唔會對胃唔好<br />\n一條粟米加一隻全蛋<br />\n而家諗住整毛豆加蛋做早餐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n橙好酸食完唔會胃痛咩<br />\n整三文治<br />\n芝士火腿咁擺落雪櫃<br />\n第二日喺雪櫃拎走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係怕酸對胃唔好 我個胃本身都敏感 但朝早食完冇胃痛<br />\n唔鐘意食火腿同芝士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c58a3c6cbec9eb59e6c36d133ea89bb2c787c9","tid":242514,"uid":23112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:46:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我最多都係三文治+果醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果醋好唔好飲 有咩功效"},{"pid":"c5c57f6abc71d32d82ad1a89788132724b741c53","tid":242514,"uid":23112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"西蘭花加雞比肉走皮得唔得<br />\n我都幾鐘意食西蘭花"}]}